Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太真抱歉  突然跑来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉没有好东西招待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  这样就很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳平常是都吃什么  我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利商店现成的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是啦  我结婚前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很会做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪会   妳舌头不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃   还可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃   那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我吃过最好吃的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我只做了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗   开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报复刚刚的玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么好的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理好吃又幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最讨厌的就是   还这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早点找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我若遇到你老婆这样的肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会说话   哪是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他离婚嫁给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂   这是我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对喔  忘了  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有女朋友吗  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都好几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会帮他介绍   我尽量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要会做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了这是我老婆   又忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了  抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是买的吗  自己做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手料理   又再开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐还好吧   像餐厅做的样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太会倒酒  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有就要偷笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太平常都做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是家庭主归   是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还没生喔?  对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛   有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢小孩吗   不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了   问题在你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想就知道问题在你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝我喝   抱歉问这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想生几个?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生还是女生  都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平常时间够用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  大部分都在做家事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会尽量早点做完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  他睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能邀请你来  他应该很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他平时不会喝这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正明天休假就让他睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  难得请你来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太太真可惜  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里平常很少有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是我有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且太太长这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要爱上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉   我好像喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吗  那样不太好
