Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会忍不住  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
