Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.90,0:38:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.88,0:39:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.89,0:39:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.97,0:39:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服  这样好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.93,0:39:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射在我嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.93,0:40:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴张开   要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.94,0:41:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要再来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.88,0:41:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.93,0:42:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的邻居太太
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.88,0:42:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.95,0:42:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.95,0:42:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.96,0:42:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.96,0:42:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.96,0:42:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要叫救护车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.96,0:42:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.97,0:42:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.91,0:42:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.98,0:43:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事我慢慢走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.99,0:43:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.92,0:43:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别勉强   我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.99,0:43:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.95,0:43:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.96,0:43:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚抬高点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.90,0:43:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉一直麻烦你  我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.91,0:43:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗  我房间很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.91,0:44:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷气坏了  我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.99,0:44:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常看到你在扫地   脏的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.93,0:44:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起   我妈妈都不会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.00,0:44:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在家都没事做
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.94,0:44:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有工作吗  我是主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.87,0:44:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.89,0:44:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳流好多汗  好热
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.96,0:44:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会感冒   要不要换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.97,0:45:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系   我待会自己换
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.91,0:45:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.91,0:45:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.92,0:45:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你换好我就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.99,0:45:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉   在后面柜子里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.00,0:45:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗  对
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.88,0:45:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T恤跟裤子就好吗   对
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.99,0:46:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先帮你脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.00,0:46:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来   没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.00,0:46:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己可以  没关系我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.88,0:46:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以  我帮你脱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.90,0:47:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.90,0:47:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换内裤  内裤不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.91,0:47:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会弄痛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.98,0:47:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.93,0:47:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.95,0:47:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.88,0:48:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.96,0:48:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到的  别打开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都用这个吗  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.90,0:48:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看  我还没用过
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.98,0:48:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来长这样  拜托别看
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.98,0:48:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.99,0:48:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.93,0:48:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在里面吗  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你当作没看到   流更多汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.94,0:49:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你擦  毛巾在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.95,0:49:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等   你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.96,0:49:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你擦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.96,0:49:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.92,0:49:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是汗昧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.95,0:50:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.97,0:50:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上很脏  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.93,0:51:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.94,0:52:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.97,0:52:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摸哪
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.98,0:53:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.99,0:53:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必动  那边...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.93,0:53:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.00,0:53:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.94,0:53:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛  要脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.90,0:53:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.96,0:54:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很脏  这里都是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.98,0:56:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么猛
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.99,0:56:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.92,0:57:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.92,0:58:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.93,0:58:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.93,0:58:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买不就是要用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.00,0:58:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.94,0:59:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.95,0:59:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.96,0:59:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.90,0:59:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.91,0:59:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.92,0:59:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.94,1:00:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗  舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.98,1:00:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太快
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.93,1:01:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗  不行怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.00,1:01:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会射吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.95,1:01:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.92,1:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.93,1:02:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很敏感吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.94,1:02:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏感吗  这样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.88,1:02:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.95,1:02:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起自慰呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.90,1:02:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗   不行不行
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.97,1:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.91,1:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.93,1:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.94,1:03:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.95,1:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.89,1:03:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行吗   不行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.90,1:03:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.98,1:04:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.00,1:04:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.95,1:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.96,1:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.97,1:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.91,1:05:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.92,1:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射就射我嘴里
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.93,1:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.01,1:05:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.95,1:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要站稳喔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.91,1:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样弄
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.98,1:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.88,1:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  站不稳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.95,1:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.89,1:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗  这样弄会腿软
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.90,1:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想口射吗  对
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.98,1:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.94,1:07:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.94,1:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站不稳了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.88,1:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒站的很稳
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.88,1:10:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射吗  射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.93,1:11:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.98,1:11:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.92,1:11:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.99,1:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我在来探病
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.00,1:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学会
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.87,1:12:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几年都没联络  就是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.88,1:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛全部攻击我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.96,1:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快吃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.90,1:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没吃  我有吃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.97,1:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.98,1:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉结婚了吧  是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.91,1:13:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.98,1:13:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的   我这么喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.99,1:13:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.00,1:13:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前不是常说吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.00,1:13:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没印象  好伤心
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.88,1:13:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.95,1:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做什么的   做金管的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.90,1:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他几岁   大我七岁
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.91,1:13:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.98,1:14:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错   干嘛一直问我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.98,1:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你要不要比较一下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.99,1:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱莉从来不谈自己嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.00,1:14:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们感情不错
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.87,1:14:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也快结婚了   骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.95,1:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.96,1:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚在说爱莉结婚了  是喔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.96,1:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁  我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.90,1:15:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来就好  等等
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.91,1:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大岛老师也结婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.98,1:15:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年也没来  好像是很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.92,1:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法嘛   做老师的都很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.93,1:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很忙啊   你不算啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.00,1:15:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么无精打采的  没有
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.95,1:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.90,1:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  老师来了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.90,1:16:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是碰碰运气  没想到还在
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.97,1:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师请坐
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.91,1:16:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校忙到晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.92,1:16:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你夸奖我也没分数喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.99,1:16:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随意就好   干杯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.94,1:16:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉前一阵子结婚了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.95,1:16:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜   老公就是我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.96,1:17:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骗人的  不是他
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.90,1:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师跟师母怎么样   干嘛问
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.97,1:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教你们都教怕了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.98,1:17:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别毕业就嚣张   抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.92,1:17:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只约了吃饭   只是吃饭
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.93,1:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你喜欢怎样的   温柔的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.01,1:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长的像野兽也行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.88,1:18:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再帮我盛   还吃喔你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.96,1:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不太会喝   你能走吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.90,1:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.91,1:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站的稳吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.99,1:18:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回去吧   好像离车站很近
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.92,1:18:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天休假
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.93,1:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以送你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.94,1:19:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用   我送就好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.88,1:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能起来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.89,1:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的包包   给我就好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.96,1:19:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也别喝醉喔   好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.90,1:19:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心老师慢走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.98,1:19:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见  老师晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.99,1:19:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.93,1:19:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.00,1:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背我  背你？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.88,1:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  走不动了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.89,1:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那就一下下
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.96,1:20:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗   好了  来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.90,1:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.91,1:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都这把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.92,1:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重吗  是我身体差
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.99,1:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  没事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.00,1:21:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也走不动了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.01,1:21:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真任性
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.88,1:21:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面吗  对
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.89,1:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家在哪  这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.89,1:21:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.89,1:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你.家好大   我就送到这吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.97,1:21:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  送我进去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.97,1:21:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.98,1:21:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公呢  今天不在
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.92,1:21:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚还不在
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.99,1:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天会很晚
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.92,1:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你到大门
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.94,1:22:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.88,1:22:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.95,1:22:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  多喝点水
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.89,1:22:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进来  到里面...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.90,1:22:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去就不太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.90,1:22:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少喝杯水  别在意
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.91,1:22:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  老师...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.97,1:22:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.98,1:23:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.00,1:23:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了  喝水  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.88,1:23:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家真的好大
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.95,1:23:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有   老公经济不错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.89,1:23:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.96,1:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他还好吗  好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.90,1:23:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你结婚了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.91,1:23:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过的好就好
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.91,1:24:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有生小孩吗  没有
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.92,1:24:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.92,1:24:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师   我...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.99,1:24:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.00,1:24:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.01,1:24:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从年级到毕业都喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.89,1:24:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗   谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.89,1:24:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到今天还能见到老师
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.91,1:25:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.99,1:25:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.00,1:25:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么   我都结婚了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.00,1:25:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能外遇
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.89,1:25:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次就好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.96,1:26:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.00,1:26:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.95,1:31:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.90,1:33:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.95,1:34:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏感吗   好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.92,1:36:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.98,1:38:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴  你这么湿
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.93,1:38:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.90,1:40:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再舔吗  再舔我
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.98,1:40:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.90,1:42:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.95,1:42:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了  不行
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.95,1:42:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.96,1:42:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.97,1:42:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.97,1:42:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了  不行
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.98,1:43:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.93,1:43:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师不行
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.00,1:43:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.94,1:43:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.95,1:43:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了   不行   要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.89,1:44:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看   坐上来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.88,1:45:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.96,1:49:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.96,1:51:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.97,1:51:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.99,1:51:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了   老师插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.00,1:52:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿   老师插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.94,1:53:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.91,1:54:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.88,1:54:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.96,1:54:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  不行
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.96,1:55:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.94,1:56:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.88,1:56:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.96,1:57:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.00,1:57:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.00,1:57:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.01,1:57:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了   去给我看
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.88,1:57:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.90,1:58:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.00,1:58:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了
