Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.93,1:59:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.94,2:00:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.96,2:00:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.96,2:00:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.90,2:00:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.91,2:00:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  已经去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.92,2:00:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.92,2:00:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.98,2:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.00,2:02:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.91,2:02:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.92,2:03:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.00,2:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.97,2:03:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.91,2:05:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒   你好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.98,2:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.93,2:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.94,2:06:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我射好吗   全射给我
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.98,2:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.96,2:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师我爱你
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.97,2:08:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.00,2:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被看见就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.88,2:10:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  会很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.95,2:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是   再陪我下好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.99,2:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.99,2:10:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉   请多指教
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.00,2:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以选喜欢的房间主
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.93,2:11:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:07.00,2:11:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳辞职了吗   是的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.87,2:11:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是间大公司  是
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.95,2:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不用辞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.95,2:11:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  这样怎么抱孙子
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.88,2:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了也要习惯家里
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.89,2:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.89,2:11:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了家里也热闹点
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.97,2:11:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太热闹会吵到邻居
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.90,2:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上也不能太太声
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.91,2:11:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早上5点就起床做早饭
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.98,2:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以脕上要安静点   好的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.98,2:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早!睡有什么差别   哪没有
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.92,2:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到我皮肤很滑吗
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.93,2:12:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我不喜欢早睡   谁管你
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.00,2:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉皮肤也很滑   没有
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.94,2:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样才有说服力
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.94,2:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么年轻当然比我好
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.95,2:12:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉会做菜吗   家常的程度
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.95,2:12:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待    我吃腻妈妈的菜了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.89,2:12:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思   不做给你吃了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.96,2:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃爱莉做的
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.97,2:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以交给你吗
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.90,2:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也想好好休自
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.97,2:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的习俗都是这样
Dialogue: 0,2:12:54.98,2:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人喜欢吃很咸
Dialogue: 0,2:12:57.91,2:13:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得别放太多   也别太油
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.99,2:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们家不太用冷气
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.92,2:13:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹电扇就好
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.93,2:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管她   当自己家就好
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.94,2:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.95,2:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉   你这是在折什么
Dialogue: 0,2:13:40.89,2:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右都不平均   这样怎么迭
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.96,2:13:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看就知道很少做家事
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.97,2:13:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去重新弄   全部都要
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.97,2:13:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是洗好的吗   油都没洗掉
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.91,2:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用点力气   我重新洗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.91,2:14:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连碗都不会洗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.99,2:14:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底会不会做人媳妇
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.99,2:14:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.89,2:14:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是...爱莉
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.96,2:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是叫你打扫吗   我做了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.96,2:14:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允许家里有灰尘
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.90,2:15:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你做事都这么随便码
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.91,2:15:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有   这个怎么办
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.98,2:15:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新擦  知道吧那就重做
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.99,2:15:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,2:15:20.99,2:15:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  别老是要我说
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.90,2:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.96,2:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是叫你包饺子吗  你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:16:07.97,2:16:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的   你不觉得丑吗
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.91,2:16:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经努力了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.98,2:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小不一样   外观也很丑
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.92,2:16:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种样子叫我怎么招待邻居
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.92,2:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么吃   你重新再做
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.93,2:16:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部?   对
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.00,2:16:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了   这么丑谁会想吃
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.94,2:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有一件事能做好
Dialogue: 0,2:16:43.87,2:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新弄   真是受不了你
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.96,2:17:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.90,2:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁今天也很晚吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.90,2:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也说是有新的企划要做
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.90,2:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结婚了还不顾着点家
Dialogue: 0,2:17:18.98,2:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在关系着升迁
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.91,2:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁是男人嘛   也不用这样吧
Dialogue: 0,2:17:34.99,2:17:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咸   味道太咸了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.93,2:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很咸吗   你自己喝
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.94,2:17:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗    咸死我了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.88,2:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还好
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.95,2:17:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得咸   舌头有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:59.95,2:18:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.89,2:18:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点点   你看吧
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.89,2:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么咸怎么喝
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.96,2:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都做不好
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.90,2:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫不行洗碗不行 料理也不行
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.90,2:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样家里怎么交给你
Dialogue: 0,2:18:28.91,2:18:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直念   还这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.91,2:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做久了就会了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:37.99,2:18:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁怎么就看上这种女人
Dialogue: 0,2:18:41.99,2:18:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂   说的太过份了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.93,2:18:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饺子很好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.00,2:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你的别啰唆  这是重故的
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.87,2:19:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不会   你别搅和了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.95,2:19:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉快吃   别管她
Dialogue: 0,2:19:10.95,2:19:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没食欲了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.89,2:22:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉  来一下
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.96,2:22:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸有事吗   鞋子...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.96,2:22:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打的蜡吗   我打过了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.90,2:22:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔  看起来不亮
Dialogue: 0,2:22:50.91,2:22:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打过了吗   抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.91,2:22:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双鞋很贵   要小心保养
Dialogue: 0,2:23:05.99,2:23:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.99,2:23:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.00,2:23:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.89,2:23:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉   来下
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.90,2:23:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了   盘子有洗吗
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.91,2:23:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我洗过了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.91,2:24:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点脏   抱歉我再去洗
Dialogue: 0,2:24:09.92,2:24:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里洗   这里?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.00,2:24:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舔的舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:24:23.00,2:24:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舌头舔把盘子干净
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.88,2:24:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做的到吧
Dialogue: 0,2:24:36.88,2:24:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是说会努力做好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:24:47.96,2:24:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.96,2:24:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会做吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.00,2:25:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样舔怎么会干净
Dialogue: 0,2:25:34.00,2:25:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.95,2:25:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样舌头伸长
Dialogue: 0,2:26:19.92,2:26:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是能做好嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.99,2:26:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.99,2:26:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了   刚刚...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.00,2:26:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了好好教你怎么舔
Dialogue: 0,2:26:39.94,2:26:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然都舔了   我的脚正好脏了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.88,2:26:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚  帮我舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:26:55.95,2:26:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这坐坐下
Dialogue: 0,2:27:12.90,2:27:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起一只脚
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.99,2:27:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对   把脏的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.99,2:27:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舔的舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:27:42.93,2:27:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吧?  回答
Dialogue: 0,2:28:10.96,2:28:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不甘愿的样子
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.90,2:28:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的舔
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.91,2:28:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚趾用吸的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.92,2:28:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我舔
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.94,2:28:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样   有没有舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.95,2:29:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,2:29:24.90,2:29:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚趾也要舔
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.98,2:29:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好   你要是做不好
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.92,2:29:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会被妈妈骂喔
Dialogue: 0,2:29:48.93,2:29:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最好听我的话
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.93,2:29:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好感激我的温柔   是
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.89,2:30:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫   对不起
Dialogue: 0,2:30:28.97,2:30:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿毛巾
Dialogue: 0,2:30:32.97,2:30:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在这
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.98,2:30:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.93,2:30:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,2:31:07.00,2:31:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔干净吧
Dialogue: 0,2:31:19.95,2:31:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把？
Dialogue: 0,2:31:27.96,2:31:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄干净    回答呢
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.96,2:31:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是    大声点
Dialogue: 0,2:31:40.90,2:31:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.91,2:31:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟刚刚一样   用舔的
Dialogue: 0,2:31:53.98,2:31:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舔干净会被骂喔
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.94,2:32:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都含住
Dialogue: 0,2:32:28.95,2:32:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,2:32:57.91,2:33:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,2:33:02.99,2:33:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被妈妈骂吧
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.00,2:33:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对   自己过来舔
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.94,2:33:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了教育你
Dialogue: 0,2:33:30.88,2:33:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也被弄脏了  舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:33:39.96,2:33:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,2:34:26.00,2:34:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,2:34:35.88,2:34:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  握住   舔蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,2:35:39.94,2:35:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用吹的   别只舔一固地方
Dialogue: 0,2:35:46.88,2:35:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,2:35:53.96,2:35:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深一点
Dialogue: 0,2:36:11.97,2:36:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,2:36:40.94,2:36:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来   站着
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.88,2:36:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,2:36:56.95,2:36:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次换我了
Dialogue: 0,2:37:04.96,2:37:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想待在这吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:24.98,2:37:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,2:37:55.95,2:37:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱    听我的话
Dialogue: 0,2:38:01.95,2:38:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,2:38:10.89,2:38:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.97,2:38:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上来
Dialogue: 0,2:38:30.91,2:38:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能躲
Dialogue: 0,2:39:04.95,2:39:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫出来没关系
Dialogue: 0,2:39:24.97,2:39:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用忍着
Dialogue: 0,2:39:51.93,2:39:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手干什么
Dialogue: 0,2:40:03.94,2:40:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想阿铁
Dialogue: 0,2:40:13.95,2:40:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我的就好
Dialogue: 0,2:41:20.95,2:41:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没被舔过吗    没被舔过脚吗
Dialogue: 0,2:41:32.96,2:41:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么美的脚
Dialogue: 0,2:41:47.91,2:41:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件也脱
Dialogue: 0,2:42:42.90,2:42:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚舔了我的
Dialogue: 0,2:42:46.90,2:42:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我也帮你舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.92,2:43:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚别夹
Dialogue: 0,2:44:55.97,2:44:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去就说出来
Dialogue: 0,2:45:02.91,2:45:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不用忍
Dialogue: 0,2:45:06.91,2:45:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很舒服吧    那不用忍
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.92,2:45:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里舔好了
