Dialogue: 0,3:06:16.98,3:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉   以后也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,3:06:44.87,3:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄结束后
Dialogue: 0,3:06:52.88,3:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,3:07:03.96,3:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没结过婚   不知道怎么演人妻
Dialogue: 0,3:07:09.97,3:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样演吧
Dialogue: 0,3:07:14.90,3:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演的很好  那就好
Dialogue: 0,3:07:17.97,3:07:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会觉得演人妻太年轻吗
Dialogue: 0,3:07:23.98,3:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对   我太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,3:07:31.99,3:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过学生好像比较适合
Dialogue: 0,3:07:38.93,3:07:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次扮演很多人妻
Dialogue: 0,3:07:46.00,3:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有最喜欢的吗
Dialogue: 0,3:08:00.95,3:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,3:08:04.95,3:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后结婚就像这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,3:08:14.96,3:08:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会跟老师偷情
Dialogue: 0,3:08:20.97,3:08:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是   会好好生活
Dialogue: 0,3:08:25.91,3:08:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果老公外遇呢
Dialogue: 0,3:08:32.98,3:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分居
Dialogue: 0,3:08:36.99,3:08:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是   谁都会的
Dialogue: 0,3:08:39.92,3:08:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后结婚   要注意喔
Dialogue: 0,3:08:45.93,3:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想结婚码   会想
Dialogue: 0,3:08:53.94,3:08:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到好对象会冲动吗
Dialogue: 0,3:08:58.88,3:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会尽量别冲动
Dialogue: 0,3:09:03.95,3:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你这样的老婆就满足了
Dialogue: 0,3:09:10.89,3:09:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道具的戒指还戴着吗   戴着
Dialogue: 0,3:09:14.89,3:09:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好看结婚会想要戒指吗
Dialogue: 0,3:09:21.96,3:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不用很贵的
Dialogue: 0,3:09:27.97,3:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是种意义
Dialogue: 0,3:09:32.91,3:09:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会想去蜜月旅行吗   可以的话
Dialogue: 0,3:09:37.98,3:09:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会办婚礼吗   有钱的话
Dialogue: 0,3:09:43.99,3:09:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啦   希望你美梦成真
Dialogue: 0,3:09:51.99,3:09:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见   辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,3:10:02.00,3:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超色人妻性幻想    铃村爱莉
Dialogue: 0,3:10:12.95,3:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本片结束
